OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778512268
OL,3,CThousands take part in Town and Gown
OL,4,CRun
OL,6,FIt was the biggest event to date in
OL,7,Fits 44-year history having sold-out
OL,8,Ffor a third consecutive year.
OL,10,FRunners are on track to collectively
OL,11,Fraise #350k for the charity, which
OL,12,Fsupports more than 110,000 children
OL,13,Fand adults in the UK living with one
OL,14,Fof over 60 muscle wasting and
OL,15,Fweakening conditions.
OL,17,FJessie Keighley, Events Manager at
OL,18,FMuscular Dystrophy UK said: "Each year
OL,19,Fthis community event continues to grow
OL,20,Fand has sold-out for the last three
OL,21,Fyears.
OL,26,@zD@]OU
