OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778512268
OL,3,CThousands take part in Town and Gown
OL,4,CRun
OL,6,FThe Bidwells Oxford 10k is the oldest
OL,7,Frun in the Town and Gown series, with
OL,8,Fthe sister event taking place in
OL,9,FCambridge, in October.
OL,11,FInspired by a local boy Daniel Cleaver
OL,12,Fwho had muscular dystrophy, it started
OL,13,Fin 1982. Daniel's father and local
OL,14,Frunners set up the event as a fun run.
OL,16,FAll profits go to supporting Muscular
OL,17,FDystrophy UK and the events have
OL,18,Fcollectively raised over #3 million.
